Body\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rld1665702628742.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rld1665702628742.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rld1665702628742.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rld1665702628742\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Use Detail Trigger\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the detail trigger (as opposed to the valueChanged trigger) is activated when the user clicks the widget.\n </p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rld1665702628742__table_d12791e1_d12792e1_d12793e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rld1665702628742__table_d12791e1_d12792e1_d12793e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rld1665702628742__table_d12791e1_d12792e1_d12793e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rld1665702628742__table_d12791e1_d12792e1_d12793e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rld1665702628742__table_d12791e1_d12792e1_d12793e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The detail trigger is activated. The value of the field is not changed and Uniface does not activate thevalueChanged trigger.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rld1665702628742__table_d12791e1_d12792e1_d12793e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rld1665702628742__table_d12791e1_d12792e1_d12793e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The value is changed and the valueChanged trigger is activated.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rld1665702628742__p_d108644e1_d108645e1_d108646e1\">This property cannot be set in ProcScript.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rld1665702628742__section_pgx_bl5_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1163078e121\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fxi1688449052174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxi1688449052174.html\" title=\"The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox.\">ucheckbox (CheckBox)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615660\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615660\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Use Detail Trigger Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Use Detail Trigger This property determines whether the detail trigger (as opposed to the valueChanged trigger) is activated when the user clicks the widget. Value Description True The detail trigger is activated. The value of the field is not changed and Uniface does not activate thevalueChanged trigger. False (default) The value is changed and the valueChanged trigger is activated. This property cannot be set in ProcScript. Applies To ucheckbox (CheckBox) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}